_sText:
This is the second map that I have made for a clan (In this case, AFC [formerly PNX]).

Features moving lasers, 10 Teleporters, A very secret sniper room ;) (Look under the AFC lettering), and a hidden weapons room that can be activated with the portal (on top of the AFC lettering).

The map starts with a glass barrier separating the two teams for the first 8 seconds of the game (Note that this includes 5 seconds buying time). This just means that players have time to get out of the towers if they want to.
